U.K. Man Gets Eight Years in $22 Million Fraud, Daily Mail Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-14T23:09:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/u-k-man-gets-eight-years-in-22-million-fraud-daily-mail-says.html
Terry Freeman, who pleaded guilty
last month to fraudulent trading in a scheme in which he
swindled as much as 14 million pounds ($22.5 million) from 300
U.K. victims, was today sentenced to eight years in prison, the
Daily Mail reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
